prompt: An adventurous anime panda exploring a hidden cave filled with ancient treasures and mystical symbols.
revised_prompt: An adventurous anime-style panda, characterized by its over-sized eyes and stylized design, venturing into the mysterious depths of a hidden cave. The cave itself is filled with wondrous ancient treasures including ornate jewelry, gold coins, mysterious artifacts, and valuable gemstones. Also present within the cave are mystical symbols, etched into cave walls, glowing subtly with an unexplained energy. Everything is slightly illuminated by the glow from these mysterious markings, casting a spectacular display of light and shadows, which amplifies the enchanting atmosphere of the cave.
